snippet.title: Life is Strange 2  - E3 2019 Celebration Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Get Life is Strange 2 here: https://sqex.link/lifeiaca6c

Episodes 1 - 3 of #LifeisStrange2 are out now on PlayStation 4!

A new chapter of Life is Strange has begun, join us on our latest emotional journey. 

After a tragic incident, brothers Sean and Daniel Diaz run away from home. Fearing the police, and dealing with Daniel's new telekinetic power, the boys head to Mexico. Each stop on their journey brings new friends and new challenges. 

Special thanks to our community and our collaborators for helping make Life is Strange what it is today. Featured in this video are:
